# Studio environment — copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in your key:
#
# This file is read for ANTHROPIC_API_KEY only. 
# Resolution order: 
# the process environment wins; .env is the fallback. The key is injected
# into the Agent SDK subprocess, never logged (pino redaction), and
# never written into workspace files. 
#
# Without it the studio runs in keyless mode: 
# library browsing, canvas review, and compliance display
# generation is disabled with guidance shown in place.
#
# Get a key: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here